jorada del cuello uterino. Su uso es detectar células no normales en el cuello uterino.','Colposcopía','','publish','closed','closed','','colposcopia','','','2017-08-22 17:02:42','2017-08-22 17:02:42','',9,'http://nomascancer.info/?page_id=181',0,'page','',0),(182,1,'2017-07-19 22:54:29','2017-07-19 22:54:29','','Colposcopia','','inherit','closed','closed','','181-revision-v1','','','2017-07-19 22:54:29','2017-07-19 22:54:29','',181,'http://nomascancer.info/181-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(183,1,'2017-07-19 22:55:06','2017-07-19 22:55:06','Nuestro examen de citología se conoce también como prueba de Papanicolau. Es un examen cuyo propósito es diagnosticar a tiempo patologías del tipo cáncer de cuello de útero. La muestra se consigue a través de una extracción con un suave raspado.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Citología','','publish','closed','closed','','citologia','','','2017-08-22 16:52:30','2017-08-22 16:52:30','',9,'http://nomascancer.info/?page_id=183',0,'page','',0),(184,1,'2017-07-19 22:55:06','2017-07-19 22:55:06','','Citología','','inherit','closed','closed','','183-revision-v1','','','2017-07-19 22:55:06','2017-07-19 22:55:06','',183,'http://nomascancer.info/183-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(185,1,'2017-07-19 22:55:19','2017-07-19 22:55:19','','Crioterapia','','publish','closed','closed','','crioterapia','','','2017-07-19 22:55:36','2017-07-19 22:55:36','',9,'http://nomascancer.info/?page_id=185',0,'page','',0),(186,1,'2017-07-19 22:55:19','2017-07-19 22:55:19','','Crioterapia','','inherit','closed','closed','','185-revision-v1','','','2017-07-19 22:55:19','2017-07-19 22:55:19','',185,'http://nomascancer.info/185-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(188,1,'2017-08-10 19:11:20','2017-08-10 19:11:20','','Inicio','','publish','closed','closed','','inicio','','','2017-11-10 03:30:06','2017-11-10 03:30:06','',0,'http://nomascancer.info/?p=188',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(189,1,'2017-08-10 19:11:20','2017-08-10 19:11:20',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','189','','